---

<footer class="mt-20 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-950">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
          <img
            src="/librehub.png"
            alt="LibreHub logo"
            class="h-8 w-auto object-contain"
          />
          <span class="font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Ανακάλυψε καλύτερα εργαλεία</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          Κατάλογος ελεύθερου και ανοιχτού κώδικα λογισμικού (ΕΛ/ΛΑΚ) για κάθε ανάγκη.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-600">
          Αναπτύσσεται από τον
          <a href="https://eiosifidis.blogspot.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 hover:underline">Ευστάθιο Ιωσηφίδη</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Πλοήγηση</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/" class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-green-600 dark:hover:text-green-400 transition-colors">Αρχική</a></li>
          <li><a href="/#categories" class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-green-600 dark:hover:text-green-400 transition-colors">Κατηγορίες</a></li>
          <li><a href="/suggest" class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-green-600 dark:hover:text-green-400 transition-colors">Προτείνετε Λογισμικό</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Resources -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Πόροι</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li>
            <a href="https://mathe.ellak.gr" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Μάθε ΕΕΛΛΑΚ (ανοίγει σε νέα καρτέλα)" class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-green-600 dark:hover:text-green-400 transition-colors flex items-center gap-1">
              Μάθε ΕΕΛΛΑΚ
              <svg class="h-3 w-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 6H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 003 8.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0018 18.75V10.5m-10.5 6L21 3m0 0h-5.25M21 3v5.25"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://opensource.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="Open Source Initiative (ανοίγει σε νέα καρτέλα)" class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-green-600 dark:hover:text-green-400 transition-colors flex items-center gap-1">
              Open Source Initiative
              <svg class="h-3 w-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 6H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 003 8.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0018 18.75V10.5m-10.5 6L21 3m0 0h-5.25M21 3v5.25"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://www.gnu.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="GNU Project (ανοίγει σε νέα καρτέλα)" class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-green-600 dark:hover:text-green-400 transition-colors flex items-center gap-1">
              GNU Project
              <svg class="h-3 w-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 6H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 003 8.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0018 18.75V10.5m-10.5 6L21 3m0 0h-5.25M21 3v5.25"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-600">
        © {new Date().getFullYear()} LibreHub. Περιεχόμενο υπό άδεια Creative Commons.
      </p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-600">
        <span>Φτιαγμένο με</span>
        <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 hover:underline">Astro</a>
        <span>&</span>
        <a href="https://tailwindcss.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 hover:underline">Tailwind CSS</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
